PrecisEnactment of the OFFSHORE MINERALS REVENUE ELECTION REGULATIONS which specify that a province referred to in subsection 4(11) of this Act (i.e., one receiving offshore petroleum royalties) shall, in each calendar year, make the election referred to in that subsection by informing the Minister of Finance, in writing, of that election.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 2000-0007 Publication Date: 2000-01-05
Attachments
precis:
Enactment of the OFFSHORE MINERALS REVENUE ELECTION REGULATIONS which
specify that a province referred to in subsection 4(11) of this Act (i.e.,
one receiving offshore petroleum royalties) shall, in each calendar year,
make the election referred to in that subsection by informing the Minister
of Finance, in writing, of that election.
